nics and original assets, Spooki Tag offers a spine-tingling multiplayer experience that pays tribute to the original game while delivering heart-pounding horror. Are you brave enough to join the chase?", "short_description": "Spooki Tag is a thrilling fan-made horror twist on the popular game Gorilla Tag. Navigate eerie maps and avoid terrifying entities lurking in the shadows. With unique mechanics and original assets, Spooki Tag offers a spine-tingling multiplayer experience that pays homage to the original while delivering heart-pounding horror. Are you brave enough to join the chase?"}]}, "developer_name": "Aero Monk Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/spooki-tag/privacy-policy?authuser=0", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "GoodSoup", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/spooki-tag/home?authuser=0", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1023770785722696"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "25995772826733410"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1965155747250132"}]}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1723258800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1965155747250132"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "263767668853006